cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Minerva: a JSON-backed slide editor for human + Claude collaboration"
message: "If you use Minerva in academic work, please cite it as below."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Ray
    given-names: Arijit
repository-code: "https://github.com/arijitray1993/minerva"
url: "https://github.com/arijitray1993/minerva"
abstract: >
  Minerva is a Google-Slides-like editor where humans and Claude collaborate
  on the same portable JSON deck file. The editor's Konva-based renderer is
  the single source of truth for layout; Claude edits deck.json directly and
  uses the editor's PNG/PDF export to see what it produced.
license: MIT
year: 2026
